item.title: Social Media
item.dc:creator: CuckooThemes
item.content:encoded: [h2]Social Media Boxes[/h2] [div-line] [toggle title="Social Media Boxes | Grab Shortcode" fold="false"][code width="100%" background="#ffffff"][one-third title="Facebook"][fb-box appId="373470946049453" user="CuckooThemes" show_stream="false"][/one-third][one-third title="Twitter"][twitter-list twitter_id="cuckoothemes" how_many="3"][/one-third][one-third last="true" title="Flickr"][flickr flickr_id="79295992@N08" count="9"][/one-third][/code][/toggle] [text-box width="100%" align="center" background]Facebook Box, Twitter Box and Flickr Box shortcodes allow you to display your social media content in CuckooTap theme CuckooTap theme does not support widgets, that’s why we created few usefull social media shortcodes to fill this gap. From now, CuckooTap V1.9 theme users can add Facebook Box, Twitter Box and Flickr Box. Each Social Media box can be customized by editing its shortcode. How to add Social Media Box shortcodes to your homepage? If you want to add these shortcodes to your homepage, create a new page and enter Social Media Box shortcodes you want.
